25/03/2008
BANJA LUKA, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- A three-year-old boy from the village of Koprivna drowned in floods that swept across northern BiH at the weekend.
Police said they found his body Monday (March 24th) after he went missing Sunday.
Heavy rains and floods damaged over 300 houses in the area.
(AP - 24/03/08)
